    <h4 id="fair-principles">FAIR Principles</h4>
    <p>With respect to scientific data management, the conceptual model can be considered to be an implementation of the <cite><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/sdata201618" title="The FAIR Guiding Principles for scientific data management and stewardship">FAIR Principles</a></cite>, which is a guiding principles to facilitate <q>Findable, Accessible, Interoperable and Reusable</q> knowledge discovery for machines.</p>


